## 🚀 Project Overview

This is a **Web-based LLM Evaluation Platform** that measures the quality of AI/LLM responses using 8 different evaluation metrics.

**Key Capabilities:**
- ✅ Single response evaluation
- ✅ Batch evaluation from Excel/JSON
- ✅ Real-time scoring with explanations
- ✅ Multiple verdict types
- ✅ Export results as Excel/CSV

