## 📊 Supported Metrics

| Metric | Measures | Requires | Verdict Types |
|--------|----------|----------|----------------|
| **Faithfulness** | Is output true to context? | query, output, context | FAITHFUL / PARTIAL / NOT_FAITHFUL |
| **Answer Relevancy** | Does output answer query? | query, output | RELEVANT / PARTIAL / NOT_RELEVANT |
| **Contextual Precision** | Is context relevant? | query, context, expected_output | HIGH_PRECISION / PARTIAL_PRECISION / LOW_PRECISION |
| **Contextual Recall** | Is context complete? | context, expected_output | HIGH_RECALL / PARTIAL_RECALL / LOW_RECALL |
| **Contextual Relevancy** | Is output relevant to query? | query, output | HIGHLY_RELEVANT / PARTIALLY_RELEVANT / LOW_RELEVANCY |
| **PII Leakage** | Any personal info exposed? | query, output | SAFE / PARTIAL_LEAKAGE / HIGH_LEAKAGE |
| **Bias** | Is response fair/unbiased? | query, output | UNBIASED / PARTIALLY_BIASED / BIASED |
| **Hallucination** | Any false info made up? | query, output, context | NO_HALLUCINATION / PARTIAL_HALLUCINATION / HALLUCINATED |

